        "Edge Rim Intensity → Rim x Intensity (B)",
        "Rim x Intensity → Base + Rim (B)",
        "Base + Rim → Master Node (Base Color)"
      ],
      "note": "Wire the complete color/shading chain"
    },
    {
      "step": 6,
      "action": "WIRE_MATERIAL_PROPERTIES",
      "connections": [
        "Smoothness → Master Node (Smoothness)",
        "Metallic → Master Node (Metallic)"
      ],
      "note": "Connect material property values"
    },
    {
